---
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 bg-accent px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-16 py-[120px] w-full">
  <h2 class="font-heading text-5xl font-bold text-accent-foreground text-center leading-[1.1] tracking-[-2px] max-w-[900px]">
    Ready to figure out what AI<br />can actually do for your business?
  </h2>

  <p class="font-body text-[17px] text-accent-foreground/80 text-center leading-relaxed max-w-[650px]">
    Book a free 30-minute discovery call. We'll talk about where you are, what might actually help, and whether we're the right people for it.
  </p>

  <a href="/contact" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-foreground px-10 py-5 font-heading text-sm font-semibold tracking-[1px] text-primary-foreground hover:bg-foreground/90 transition-colors">
    BOOK YOUR FREE CALL
    <ArrowRight className="h-[18px] w-[18px]" />
  </a>

  <p class="font-body text-sm text-accent-foreground/65 text-center">
    Or explore our service packages to see what's possible and what it costs.
  </p>
</section>
